'''對法輪功的鎮壓'''，或称'''對法轮功的迫害'''，指在時任[[中國共產黨中央委員會總書記|中共中央總書記]][[江澤民|江澤民]]領導下的[[中國共產黨|中國共產黨]]執政當局自1999年起實施的種種鎮壓措施。中共政府在禁止並取締[[法輪功|法輪功]]後，對法輪功所採取的措施包括多方面的[[政治宣傳|宣傳]]輿論攻勢、强制再教育， 一些看法还認為包括多種具有法律性争议的強制措施，包括滋擾性隨機拘捕、[[劳动改造|强制劳动]]、酷刑，据称有修煉者因此死亡。[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]指出，中國共產黨政府的手段目的在於通過政治宣傳、監禁、強制思想改造等手段「滅絕、根除」法輪功群體，有些法輪功學員因此死亡。<ref name="Amnesty13">{{Cite web|title=China: The crackdown on Falun Gong and other so-called "heretical organizations"|url=http://www.refworld.org/docid/3b83b6e00.html|access-date=17 March 2010|date=23 March 2000|publisher=Amnesty International}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|first=Mickey|last=Spiegel|url=http://hrw.org/reports/2002/china/|title=Dangerous Meditation: China's Campaign Against Falungong|publisher=Human Rights Watch|year=2002|accessdate=28 September 2007|isbn=1-56432-269-6|ref=harv|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403203135/https://www.hrw.org/reports/2002/china/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Tong20123">Banding after the Ban: the underground Falungong in China, 1999–2011 Tong, James W.著 Journal of Contemporary China. Nov 2012, Vol. 21 Issue 78, p1045-1062.</ref>美智庫[[哈德遜研究所|哈德遜研究所]]宗教自由中心主任指出，中共對法輪功的迫害是[[群體滅絕罪|群體滅絕罪]]<ref>{{cite news |title=The CCP Wages a Second Genocide — against Falun Gong|date =2022-02-04|language = en|publisher =《National Review》 |author=Nina Shea[[哈德遜研究所|哈德遜研究所]]宗教自由中心主任|url= https://www.nationalreview.com/2022/02/the-ccp-wages-a-second-genocide-against-falun-gong/}}</ref>。聯合國人權高級專員辦公室官網2021年6月14日刊登，12名聯合國獨立人權專家包括至少8位特別報告員聯合聲明，對於在中國被拘留的法輪功修煉者與少數群體遭到活摘器官的許多指控報告，感到極度震驚；專家團指出，早在2006、2007年，聯合國人權專家就曾向中共當局提出強行活摘囚犯器官的擔憂，但遺憾北京當時的回應缺乏相關數據，例如器官分配等待時間、或器官來源資訊等數據；專家團呼籲中方迅速回應活摘器官的指控，並允許國際人權機制進行獨立監督。<ref>{{cite news |title=China: UN human rights experts alarmed by ‘organ harvesting’ allegations|date =14 June 2021|language = |publisher =[[UNHR|UNHR]] |url= https://www.ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/DisplayNews.aspx?NewsID=27167&LangID=E}}</ref>

法轮功是由李洪志创立的气功修炼法，主要特点为将练气、冥想、道德及哲学相结合。在20世纪90年代的高速发展时期，中共政府于1999年7月20日发起“取缔”法轮功的运动。{{sfn|Spiegel|2002}}早期，法轮功曾一度被中國氣功科學研究會吸收，[[胡耀邦|胡耀邦]]「三不政策」认为对气功（包括法轮功）虽不鼓励也不应批评。实际上官媒一度正面報導、[[國家體育運動委員會|國家體育運動委員會]]也表示过支持过法轮功。1999年6月10日，中共中央總書記江澤民下令设置机構[[610辦公室|610辦公室]]，<ref name="CECC20083">Congressional-Executive Commission on China (31 October 2008) [http://www.cecc.gov/publications/annual-reports/2008-annual-report ‘Annual Report 2008’] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cecc.gov/publications/annual-reports/2008-annual-report|date=20141207021417}} Retrieved 24 December 2013.</ref>調動了國家官方媒體、司法、警察、軍隊、教育系統和事業機構，<ref name="wildgrass3">{{cite book|last=Johnson|first=Ian|title=Wild Grass: Three Portraits of Change in Modern China|year=2005|publisher=Vintage|location=New York, NY|isbn=0375719199|url=http://www.amazon.com/Wild-Grass-Portraits-Change-Modern/dp/0375719199|access-date=2016-05-18|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919212810/https://www.amazon.com/Wild-Grass-Portraits-Change-Modern/dp/0375719199|dead-url=no}}</ref>並通過電視、報紙、廣播和（此后的）互聯網的大規模宣傳及大规模管控以推動相关政策。<ref name="Leung3">Leung, Beatrice (2002) 'China and Falun Gong: Party and society relations in the modern era', Journal of Contemporary China, 11:33, 761 – 784</ref>有分析称存在系統性[[酷刑|酷刑]]<ref name="heretical3">(23 March 2000) [https://web.archive.org/web/20030711022606/http://web.amnesty.org/library/Index/engASA170112000 The crackdown on Falun Gong and other so-called ''heretical organizations''], Amnesty International</ref><ref name="orgharv3">[[David_Kilgour|David Kilgour]], [[David_Matas|David Matas]] (6 July 2006, revised 31 January 2007)  [http://organharvestinvestigation.net An Independent Investigation into Allegations of Organ Harvesting of Falun Gong Practitioners in China] {{Wayback|url=http://organharvestinvestigation.net/|date=20171208015223}} (free in 22 languages) organharvestinvestigation.net</ref>、[[非法拘禁|非法拘禁]]、[[強迫勞動|強迫勞動]]、[[對中國共產黨摘取法輪功學員及良心犯器官的指控|活摘器官]]<ref name="orgharv">[[David_Kilgour|David Kilgour]], [[David_Matas|David Matas]] (6 July 2006, revised 31 January 2007)  [http://organharvestinvestigation.net An Independent Investigation into Allegations of Organ Harvesting of Falun Gong Practitioners in China] (free in 22 languages) organharvestinvestigation.net</ref>和濫用精神病醫療措施，藉以迫使修煉者宣布放棄對法輪功的信仰。{{sfn|Spiegel|2002}}第一位獲准入中國調查的[[聯合國|聯合國]]酷刑問題特派專員[[曼弗瑞德·諾瓦克|曼弗瑞德·諾瓦克]]報告指出，酷刑在中國普遍存在，66％受害者是法轮功學員。<ref>{{cite news |author=項程鎮 |title=前聯合國官員：中國官員殘害人群 台可逮捕 |url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/556454/print |newspaper=台灣[[自由時報|自由時報]] |date=2012-01-27 |quote=諾瓦克是首位獲准進入中國調查酷刑的聯合國官員，六年前他發表赴中國實地調查報告，指出「酷刑在中國普遍存在，其中六十六％是法轮功學員」；外傳[[中華人民共和國政府|中華人民共和國政府]]活摘法轮功學員器官，他強調：「可信度（credible）極高」。}}</ref>

[[美國總統|美國總統]][[唐納·川普|川普]]2019年在白宮接見法輪功學員聽取受迫害情況<ref>{{cite news |title=Rti 中央廣播電臺 川普接見宗教迫害受害者 包括新疆維吾爾穆斯林 |url=https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2027766 |work=(台灣)中央廣播電台 |date=2019-07-18 |accessdate=2021-06-07 |archive-date=2021-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210607142643/https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2027766 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，國務卿[[邁克·蓬佩奧|邁克·蓬佩奧]]2020年聲明呼籲中共立刻停止21年「太久的迫害」、「邪惡踐踏和虐待」<ref name="VOA20200720">{{cite news |title=停止邪惡打壓：美國國務卿就中共鎮壓法輪功21週年發表聲明 |url=https://www.voacantonese.com/a/pompeo-falun-gong-statement-20200720/5511171.html |work=美國之音 |date=2020-07-20 |accessdate=2021-06-07 |archive-date=2021-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210607140134/https://www.voacantonese.com/a/pompeo-falun-gong-statement-20200720/5511171.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年5月《年度國際宗教自由報告》發佈會上， 國務卿布林肯點名制裁一名迫害法輪功的中共四川省成都市前[[610辦公室|610辦公室]]主任余輝，他和他的直系親屬將被禁止入境美國<ref>{{cite news|title =国务卿安东尼·布林肯就发布2020年度国际宗教自由报告发表讲话|date =2021-05-12|language =|publisher =[[美国国务院|美国国务院]] 新闻简报室|url =https://www.state.gov/translations/chinese/%E5%9B%BD%E5%8A%A1%E5%8D%BF%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%9C%E5%B0%BC%C2%B7%E5%B8%83%E6%9E%97%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%832020%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%8A%A5/|accessdate =2021-06-07|archive-date =2021-06-07|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210607164351/https://www.state.gov/translations/chinese/%E5%9B%BD%E5%8A%A1%E5%8D%BF%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%9C%E5%B0%BC%C2%B7%E5%B8%83%E6%9E%97%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%832020%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%8A%A5/|dead-url =no}}</ref>有观察家推估，目前至少还有数十万乃至数百万的法轮功学员因拒绝放弃信仰而被关押在再教育营、监狱或其他拘留地点。<ref name="CECC20083" /><ref name="Departmentof2">{{cite web|title=China (includes Tibet, Hong Kong, and Macau)|url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/j/drl/rls/hrrpt/2009/eap/135989.htm}}</ref>曾遭關押的法轮功学员称，法輪功學員在勞教營總是受到“最長刑期、最糟待遇”。<ref name="HumanRights3">Human Rights Watch [http://www.hrw.org/reports/2005/china1205/6.htm V. Abuses Against Petitioners in Beijing] of  report [http://www.hrw.org/reports/2005/china1205/ "We Could Disappear at Any Time"] December  2005</ref><ref>Leeshai Lemish, [http://network.nationalpost.com/np/blogs/fullcomment/archive/2008/10/07/leeshai-lemish-the-games-are-over-the-persecution-continues.aspx "The Games are Over, the Persecution Continues"] {{Wayback|url=http://network.nationalpost.com/np/blogs/fullcomment/archive/2008/10/07/leeshai-lemish-the-games-are-over-the-persecution-continues.aspx|date=20110714160556}}, National Post  7 October 2008</ref>在某些拘留所中，法轮功学员往往占据被拘留者的绝大多数。有报道指出，截至2009年，至少有2000名法轮功学员在其迫害运动中被折磨致死。<ref>Andrew Jacobs. [https://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/28/world/asia/28china.html 'China Still Presses Crusade Against Falun Gong'], New York Times, 27 April 2009.</ref> 有国际观察员和司法机构直接将反对法轮功的运动称为[[种族灭绝|种族灭绝]]。<ref>Samuel Totten and Paul Robert Bartrop ''Dictionary of Genocide''. (Greewood publishing group: 2008), p 69</ref><ref>''The Standard''. [http://www.thestandard.com.hk/news_detail.asp?we_cat=4&art_id=1779&sid=4663428&con_type=1&d_str=20050921 'Rights lawyers look to UN over plight of Falun Gong'] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017095220/http://www.thestandard.com.hk/news_detail.asp?we_cat=4&art_id=1779&sid=4663428&con_type=1&d_str=20050921|date=17 October 2015}}, 21 September 2005.</ref> 2009年，西班牙和阿根廷地方法院以种族灭绝和反人类罪起诉中共高官，指控他们在策划迫害法轮功负有责任。<ref name="reutersflg2">Reuters, [https://www.reuters.com/article/us-argentina-china-falungong-idUSTRE5BM02B20091223 "Argentine judge asks China arrests over Falun Gong"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203212405/https://www.reuters.com/article/2009/12/23/us-argentina-china-falungong-idUSTRE5BM02B20091223|date=3 December 2015}}, 22 December 2009.</ref><ref>Genocide Prevention Network, [http://www.genocidepreventionnow.org/GPNSearchResults/tabid/64/ctl/DisplayArticle/mid/400/aid/151/Default.aspx 'Spanish Court Indicts Chinese Leaders for Persecution of Falun Gong'].</re