这件事触动了中共高层與时任中共中央总书记[[江泽民|江泽民]]的神经。当晚，江泽民向其他中共领导人写信称：“难道我们共产党人所具有的[[马克思主义|马克思主义]]理论，所信奉的[[唯物论|唯物论]]、[[无神论|无神论]]，还战胜不了法轮功所宣扬的那一套东西吗？”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64184/64185/180138/10818650.html|title=江泽民文选第二卷--党和国家主要领导人选集、文选、专集--中国共产党新闻|publisher=人民网}}</ref>{{Dead link}}

=== 中共高層內部分歧===
法轮功把[[江泽民|江泽民]]个人视作鎮壓决定的负责人。<ref name=peerman />1999年7月20日，中共中央总书记[[江泽民|江泽民]]决定鎮壓法轮功，但是[[中共中央政治局常委|中共中央政治局常委]]中，[[李鹏|李鹏]]、[[朱镕基|朱镕基]]、[[李瑞环|李瑞环]]和[[胡锦涛|胡锦涛]]认为江泽民使用了错误的策略<ref>Lam, Willy Wo-Lap.CNN, 5 February 2001[http://articles.cnn.com/2001-02-05/world/china.willycolumn_1_falun-gong-sect-jiang-leadership/2?_s=PM:asiapcf "China's sect suppression carries a high price"]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

[[中国共產黨|中国共產黨]]高層內部，最初對於是否支持[[江澤民|江澤民]]鎮壓法轮功的有嚴重分歧<ref name="dangerous">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hrw.org/sites/default/files/reports/CHINA0102.pdf|title=Dangerous Meditation: China's Campaign Against Falungong|last=Spiegel|first=Mickey|coauthors=Joseph Saunders, Sidney Jones, Malcolm Smart, Jim Ross|date=2002年1月|publisher=Human Rights Watch|accessdate=17 March 2010|archive-date=2016-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509150643/https://www.hrw.org/sites/default/files/reports/CHINA0102.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2015年中华人民共和国退休軍官[[辛子陵|辛子陵]]被採訪，表示[[中国共产党中央政治局常务委员会#十五屆一中全會（1997年9月）|政治局7名常委]]中有6位不贊成，[[江澤民|江澤民]]在常委通不過鎮壓決定，江又另外開會貫徹其鎮壓主張<ref>{{cite news|author1=[[新唐人|新唐人]]記者秦雪採訪|title=專訪辛子陵：江澤民一定會受到歷史審判|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/15/4/21/n4416433.htm|publisher=[[大紀元時報|大紀元時報]]|date=2015-04-21|accessdate=2016-05-18|archive-date=2019-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123010421/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/15/4/21/n4416433.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>；[[中國共產黨|中國共產黨]]前總書記[[趙紫陽|趙紫陽]]政治秘書[[鮑彤|鮑彤]]亦曾於公開指責在權者在位者「荒唐」<ref>{{cite news|title=專訪鮑彤：修煉法輪功沒有錯 鎮壓者喪心病狂|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/15/4/24/n4418951.htm|publisher=[[大紀元時報|大紀元時報]]|date=2015-04-24}}</ref>。

2000年4月一家中國官方直屬雜誌刊文批評鎮壓政策，指「法轮功之所以在中国出现爆炸性增长，就是因为它能满足普通人的需要」。前總書記[[胡耀邦|胡耀邦]]的政治秘書[[林牧|林牧]]指中共高層對是否鎮壓法輪功態度歧異，抨擊江澤民的政策是「荒謬」，當時[[李瑞環|李瑞環]]、[[朱鎔基|朱鎔基]]、[[胡錦濤|胡錦濤]]等人都和江持不同意見，且高層幹部及家屬煉法輪功的不在少數，並指出[[425上訪事件|425上訪事件]]和平合法<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/30329-20000414.html|title=中国官方杂志批评镇压法轮功|work=RFA[[自由亞洲電台|自由亞洲電台]]|date=2000-04-14|accessdate=2016-05-18|archive-date=2015-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404065332/http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/30329-20000414.html/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/5/14/n1317661.htm|title=訪林牧：中共高層對待法輪功內幕|work=[[大紀元時報|大紀元時報]]|date=2006-05-14|accessdate=2016-05-18|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402134340/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/5/14/n1317661.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年4月，在[[王立軍事件|王立軍事件]]、[[薄熙來事件|薄熙來事件]]後，中國的網絡監控不尋常地解禁「[[六四事件|六四事件]]、[[趙紫陽|趙紫陽]]、法輪功、[[對中共摘取法輪功學員及良心犯器官的指控|活摘器官]]、轉法輪」等關鍵字，等到[[胡錦濤|胡錦濤]]出訪國外期間，「親薄熙來勢力反擊」又嚴加控制、刪除敏感訊息。北京的一位政治學者陳子明認為這體現了中共高層在法輪功問題上的鬥爭<ref name=BBC20150512>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/chinese_news/2012/04/120406_china_internet_openandshut.shtml|title=網絡封殺與解禁暴露中共權斗激烈|author=BBC國際媒體觀察部|work=[[BBC|BBC]]英國廣播公司|date=2012-04-06|accessdate=2016-05-18|archive-date=2012-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120409182131/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/chinese_news/2012/04/120406_china_internet_openandshut.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年4月中國媒體曝光遼寧[[馬三家女子勞教所|馬三家女子勞教所]]酷刑虐待勞教人員做出「突破性報道」《走出馬三家》，中國政府則否認此說法，一些中國媒體和記者公開挑戰[[中宣部|中宣部]]禁令<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/china/2013/05/130502_ana_liaoning_masanjia.shtml|title=分析：馬三家酷刑報道顯示中共內部分歧|author=BBC國際媒體觀察部|work=[[BBC|BBC]]英國廣播公司 |date=2013-05-12}}</ref>。

==對鎮壓法輪功起因的探討==
国际观察家尝试从多个角度来解释中国政府镇压法轮功的原因，包括法轮功的流行、法轮功独立于政府并拒绝听中国政府的话、中国政府内部权力斗争、以及法轮功的道德和精神内涵与[[无神论|无神论]]的马克思主义不相容。例如{{Who|有西方学者|time=2020-5-23}}认为，“[[江泽民|江泽民]]个人對於法輪功和李洪志廣受歡迎感到妒忌和愤怒”，以及“江泽民决心要以[[马克思主义|马克思主义]]与法輪功作[[意識形態|意識形態]]斗争的需要，是隨後發生的鎮壓運動的原因所在”。<ref name=peerman>Dean Peerman,[http://www.christiancentury.org/article/2004-08/china-syndrome China syndrome: the persecution of Falun Gong] {{Wayback|url=http://www.christiancentury.org/article/2004-08/china-syndrome |date=20131203021856 }}, Christian Century, 10 August 2004</ref><ref name=Saich>Tony Saich, ''Governance and Politics in China,'' Palgrave Macmillan; 2nd Ed edition (27 February 2004)</ref>

{{fact|新华社声明：「法轮功反对中国共产党和中央政府，追求理想主义、有神论和封建迷信」<ref name="english.peopledaily.com.cn">[http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/english/199908/02/enc_19990802001003_TopNews.htmlXinhua Commentary on Political Nature of Falun Gong], People's Daily, 2 August 1999</ref>，并且新华社断定，法轮功的[[真善忍|真善忍]]原理与中国共产党努力实现的[[社会主义道德|社会主义道德]]理念和文化进步没有丝毫共同点，因此有必要铲除法轮功，以维护共产党的先进地位和纯洁性。<ref name=hanson1999>Gayle M.B. Hanson, [http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1571/is_31_15/ai_55553470China Shaken by Mass Meditation – meditation movement Falun Gong] {{Wayback|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1571/is_31_15/ai_55553470China |date=20200328003036 }}, Insight on the News, 23 August 1999</ref>在镇压起初，其他发表在中国国家级媒体上的评论也声称法轮功必须被打败，因为法轮功的[[有神论|有神论]]哲学与[[辩证唯物主义|马列唯物主义]]不相容。<ref name=hanson1999 />}}{{vs}}

Willy Wo-Lap Lam在[[CNN|CNN]]写道，江泽民可能希望通过[[文革|文革]]式运动迫使高级官员对他效忠以增强自己的权威，从而在接下起的[[中共十六大|中共十六大]]中占据支配他们；<ref>Lam, Willy Wo-Lap.CNN, 5 February 2001[http://articles.cnn.com/2001-02-05/world/china.willycolumn_1_falun-gong-sect-jiang-leadership/2?_s=PM:asiapcf "China's sect suppression carries a high price"]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}，{{quotation|"By unleashing a Mao-style movement, Jiang is forcing senior cadres to pledge allegiance to his line," said the party veteran. "This will boost Jiang's authority -- and may give him enough momentum to enable him to dictate events at the pivotal 16th Communist Party congress next year."}}</ref>[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]报导声称并非所有[[中国共产党中央政治局常务委员会|政治局常委]]就法轮功必须被消灭这个论点与总书记[[江泽民|江泽民]]有共识，<ref name="ReidG">Reid, Graham (29 April-5 May 2006)[http://www.listener.co.nz/issue/3442/features/5972/nothing_left_to_lose.html "Nothing left to lose"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.listener.co.nz/issue/3442/features/5972/nothing_left_to_lose.html |date=20070930160710 }}, ''New Zealand Listener''. Retrieved 6 July 2006.</ref>但政治局中也并没有对江泽民的决定作有力抵制。<ref name=Tong>{{cite journal| first=James| last=Tong| title=An Organizational Analysis of the Falun Gong: Structure, Communications, Financing| journal=[[The_China_Quarterly|The China Quarterly]]| volume=171|pages=636–660| doi=10.1017/S0009443902000402|date=September 2002}}</ref>

中国政府保护五个政府许可的“爱国”宗教，未登记的其它宗教是在政府许可的宗教之外，容易受到镇压。<ref>Congressional Executive Commission on China, [http://www.cecc.gov/pages/annualRpt/annualRpt10/CECCannRpt2010.pdf 'Annual Report 2010'] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110203065303/http://www.cecc.gov/pages/annualRpt/annualRpt10/CECCannRpt2010.pdf |date=2011-02-03 }}, 10 October 2010, p 19.</ref>[[加拿大|加拿大]][[环球邮报|环球邮报]]报导声称，任何未在中国政府控制之下的团体均被视作一个威胁。<ref>The Globe and Mail, Beijing v. falun gong, Metro A14, 26 January 2001</ref>

华尔街日报的{{tsl|en|Craig S. Smith|克莱格·史密斯}}称，中国政府没有精神信仰，欠缺在道德上战胜精神对手的信誉，故对任何挑战其意识形态且有能力组织自己的信仰体系感到威胁。<ref name=nyt20000430>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2000/04/30/weekinreview/the-world-rooting-out-falun-gong-china-makes-war-on-mysticism.html?pagewanted=all |title=Rooting Out Falun Gong; China Makes War on Mysticism |first=Craig S.|last=Smith|work=New York Times |date=30 April 2000}}</ref>Julia Ching在American Asian Review表示，“代表中国传统宗教复兴的法轮功信仰体系，被众多中共党员和军队成员所奉行，这个事实特别令江泽民感到困扰；江泽民把法轮功视作在意识形态领域对中国政府崇尚斗争的[[无神论|无神论]]和[[历史唯物主义|历史唯物主义]]构成威胁的精神信仰；希望在政府和军队消灭这样的精神信仰。”<ref name=XIX>Julia Ching, "The Falun Gong: Religious and Political Implications", ''American Asian Review'', Vol. XIX, no. 4, Winter 2001, p. 12{{quotation|Jiang accepts the threat of Falun Gong as an ideological one: spiritual beliefs against militant atheism and historical materialism. He [wished] to purge the government and the military of such beliefs.}}</ref>

Yuezhi Zhao认为，法轮功学员已经建立了一种“抵制身份”（resistance identity），与中国社会盛行的对金钱、权力、科学理性的追求以及中国现代化的整个价值体系相对立。<ref name="zhao">Zhao Yuezhi, [http://books.google.com/?id=tiFY59xGHBkC&pg=PA209&dq=Falun+Gong,+Identity,+and+the+Struggle+over+Meaning+Inside+and+Outside+China&cd=1#v=onepage&q=Falun%20Gong%2C%20Identity%2C%20and%20the%20Struggle%20over%20Meaning%20Inside%20and%20Outside%20ChinaFalun Gong, Identity, and the Struggle over Meaning Inside and Outside China], in “Contesting Media Power: Alternative Media in a Networked World,” Nick Couldry and James Curran (ed.), (Lanham, MD: Rowman & Littlefield, 2003). ISBN 978-0-7425-2385-2</ref>Sumner B Twiss认为，“在中国，法轮功是中国本土的精神和道德传统的一个文化复兴运动，与中国政府的中国特色马克思主义完全对立。”<ref name="twiss">Twiss, Sumner B. "Religious Intolerance in Contemporary China, Including the Curious Case of Falun Gong" in ''The World's Religions After September 11.'' Arvind Sharma (ed), Greenwood Publishing, 2009 pp. 227–240</ref>

Vivienne Shue写道，“法轮功展现了对共产党合法性的全面挑战。”<ref name=Shue>Vivienne Shue, "Legitimacy Crisis in China?" In Peter Hays Gries and Stanley Rosen (eds.), State and Society in 21st-century China. Crisis, Contention, and Legitimation, (New York: RoutledgeCurzon, 2004.{{quotation| similarly writes that Falun Gong presented a comprehensive challenge to the Communist Party's legitimacy. Shue argues that Chinese rulers historically have derived their legitimacy from a claim to possess an exclusive connection to the "Truth". In imperial China, truth was based on a Confucian and Daoist cosmology, where in the case of the Communist Party, the truth is represented by Marxist-Leninism and historical materialism. Falun Gong challenged the Marxist-Leninism paradigm, reviving an understanding based on more traditionally Buddhist or Daoist conceptions.}}</ref>David Ownby 也同意法轮功构成了共产党对中华民族统治地位的挑战，法轮功唤起了一种与中国政府不同的中国传统和当代价值观，令中国政府感受到威胁，因为法轮功否定了中国政府对中国民族主义和中国人作所谓定义的唯一权力。<ref>David Ownby, "China's War Against Itself". New York Times, 15 February 2001.{{quotation|[Falun Gong's] evocation of a different vision of Chinese tradition and its contemporary value is now so threatening to the state and party because it denies them the sole right to define the meaning of Chinese nationalism, and perhaps of Chineseness."}}</ref>

