stioned Again by UN Special Rapporteurs: FalunHR Reports] {{Wayback|url=http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/chinas-organ-harvesting-questioned-again-by-un-special-rapporteurs-falunhr-reports-853799.htm |date=20161025084003 }} Retrieved 26 October 2014</ref>。
 
